Browser POSTS note text to the server when submit is clicked:

browser -> server : HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note

Browser GETS html page from the server with new note:

browser -> server : HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/notes

Server serves html page to display on browser :

server > browser : text/html @ /example/notes

Browser GETS css file from server & renders css:

browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css

server-->browser: main.css

Browser GETS main.js file from server & runs JS code:

browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.js

server-->browser: main.js

PAGE IS NOW UPDATED WITH NEW NOTE AND HAS RE-RENDERED ALL ASSETS







